PUBLICATIONS
Landscape Block Division; Tehran, Iran, Dec 2021
Yasin Delavar, Amirhossein Delavar, Dividing land into desired parcels concerning cut trees, fixed constructed
buildings on the block, and the property area. Includes three stages: block road selection (divide-conquer method),
parcel division (genetic algorithm), new building selection, and placement in each parcel (genetic algorithm). Block
road selection divides blocks into halves concerning cut trees and size equality or access of each part to that new
road. Parcel division splits each prior mini-block into a predicted number of parcels concerning cut trees and parcels
area and count. Unique building selection and placement try to choose an appropriate-sized building and align it
with the main road on the parcel concerning the feasibility of construction. A short hugging face demo is provided
only for its first road selection part.
Article manuscript in progress, to be submitted for publication in spring 2023
Related: heavy OpenCV processing, python OOP, Genetic Algorithm (PyGAD).
